<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>OTP Verification</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .email-container {
            max-width: 650px;
            margin: 30px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
            overflow: hidden;
            border: 1px solid #e6e6e6;
        }

        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4caf50, #2e7d32);
            color: #ffffff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px 15px;
        }

        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }
        .email-header {
            background-color: #28a745; /* AgroSphere's Green */
            padding: 20px;
            color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .email-content {
        	padding: 25px 20px;
            margin-top: 25px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #333333;
        }
        .otp-box {
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: 700;
            padding: 15px 25px;
            background-color: #e0f7e9; /* Light Green Background */
            border-radius: 8px;
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 20px 0px;
            color: #28a745; /* AgroSphere's Green */
            border: 2px solid #28a745;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 40px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #888888;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #28a745;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .footer p {
            margin: 5px 0;
        }
        .email-content p {
        	text-align:left;
            margin: 10px 0;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>OTP Verification for Case View</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="email-content">
            <p>Hello Customer,</p>
            <p>We received a request to verify your account with AgroSphere. Please use the OTP below to complete your verification process:</p>
            <div class="otp-box">
                {OTP_VALUE}
            </div>
            <p>This OTP is valid for the next 10 minutes. Please enter it as soon as possible.</p>
            <p>If you did not request this verification, please ignore this email or contact support.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; 2025 AgroSphere. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>Need help? <a href="https://agno-dev-ed.develop.my.site.com/agrospehre/s/contact-us">Contact Support</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>